{"tid":750093,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"野生氧氣美女仙氣逼人 47歲李英愛逆生長超驚人","createTime":"2018-07-20T14:52:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T23:31:19.000Z","uid":9573,"like":10,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"19b24cb7884bc481a7cc16cf5dab098e7a78b07d","tid":750093,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T14:52:48.000Z","msg":"「氧氣美女」李英愛即使47歲，依舊維持空靈氣質，外型也保養得宜，近日有網友在酒店的餐廳巧遇她，雖然她帶著草帽遮住大半張臉，但仍一眼被認出，而她也會跟餐廳的職員打招呼，相當親切沒架子。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-zGZDYQ21FZM/Wn0TALCzmgI/AAAAAAAAG6A/Ot4HLUERh0EYUSA1MXfeZZ6pUUCNuh5YwCLcBGAs/s1600/chrome-white1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-zGZDYQ21FZM%2FWn0TALCzmgI%2FAAAAAAAAG6A%2FOt4HLUERh0EYUSA1MXfeZZ6pUUCNuh5YwCLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2Fchrome-white1.png&h=0af5574a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網友捕獲李英愛，大讚皮膚超白。<br />\n<br />\n穿著碎花連身裙的李英愛，現身某酒店的餐廳，為了掩人耳目，她戴上草帽，不過仍擋不住明星氣場，一眼被粉絲認出，網友大讚李英愛皮膚好白，而且相當親切，會跟餐廳的職員打招呼。其實，日前就有健身中心的職員，在IG曬出李英愛上健身中心的照片。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.francosgym.com/photo3/IMG_6722.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.francosgym.com%2Fphoto3%2FIMG_6722.JPG&h=cead05c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李英愛到健身中心運動。<br />\n<br />\n素顏的李英愛跟著教練扭腰做伸展動作，姿勢十分標準，而她穿上緊身運動衣，展現纖腰細腿好身材，完全看不出47歲年紀，皮膚嫩白零瑕疵，令人驚艷。"},{"pid":"0ae2d27bac6fcbdeb49a599741561d9533823854","tid":750093,"uid":37431,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T14:53:27.000Z","msg":"係未好撚好笑?"},{"pid":"42744af58c7224c5db07b456ed00d6a6a57b31f6","tid":750093,"uid":171598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T14:53:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14d114d6f222ec4cddaa88e0c951f3c25c3f9972","tid":750093,"uid":165339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T14:58:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aa5bdcbc5312df941d7c4b2eb0dc72cf82ae308","tid":750093,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T15:00:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f43c32da34c47d5b4341c8bb4ac2bc8f0b642be0","tid":750093,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T15:00:34.000Z","msg":"胡師傅~又推甩兩件"},{"pid":"93a55fc9b14dd4d3bda0083392cef90c3569ef52","tid":750093,"uid":194560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T23:22:29.000Z","msg":"笑左 皮膚白個到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a02a82c4cc35896e7965aace8ec94b45dbe59c70","tid":750093,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T23:31:19.000Z","msg":"屌你老母無圖"}]}